<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB09167</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT TO CONSTRUCT PEDESTRIAN OVERPASS IN ALL NATIONAL ROADS WITH PRIVATE OR PUBLIC SCHOOLS AND APPROPRIATING FUNDS THEREFOR</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Provides for the construction of overpass in every or nearby school situated along a national road or highway to allow pedestrians safe crossing over busy roads without interrupting the smooth flow of vehicle traffic.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>SALCEDA, JOEY SARTE</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2019-03-12</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON PUBLIC WORKS AND HIGHWAYS ON 2019-05-20</td></tr></table>